    "objective": "“In this study, we examined the effect of CYP2C9/19 mutations on the stereoselective hydroxylation of PHT and performed a population pharmacokinetic analysis in medium-sized Japanese adult patients with epilepsy who were receiving long-term PHT therapy”",
